<typeStatus box="[1219,1271,1499,1523]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">type</typeStatus>
species name.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[192,707,1547,1572]" box="[192,707,1547,1572]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,432,1547,1571]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">Species included.</emphasis>
Only the 
<typeStatus box="[553,606,1548,1572]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">type</typeStatus>
species.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="38.[192,831,1596,1620]" box="[192,831,1596,1620]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,380,1596,1620]" pageId="38" pageNumber="37">Parent taxon.</emphasis>
Subtribe Hesperiina Latreille, 1809.
</paragraph>
